path.desc: This shape serve as reference to force paths2openscad to keep objects coordinaites. It MUST be included in generated scad files, its relative position will be used. Its only mandatory caracteristic is that the center MUST be at coord [0,0]
This opening must be large enough for JK connectors of servos.
